# TDD GREEN PHASE SKILL

## Goal
Make an existing failing test pass with minimal implementation.

## Input
- A failing test

## Output
- Minimal production code that makes the test pass

## Rules
- Only write production code
- Do NOT modify tests
- Do NOT refactor
- Do NOT add extra features or behaviors

## Constraints
- Implementation must strictly satisfy existing test only
- No speculative or future-proof code allowed